Postgrey - ChangeLog
====================

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.2.0
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Enhancement: Automatically install distribution packages
    Fixed: Delay restart of Postgrey policy server on i-MSCP upgrade/reconfiguration
    Fixed: Stop and disable Postgrey policy server on plugin deactivation
    Removed: Support for i-MSCP 1.3.x Serie

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.1.1
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Updated for i-MSCP Serie 1.3.x

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.1.0
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Added: Configuration parameter (postgrey_port) which allows to setup postgrey listening port
    Fixed: Show Postrey service port in i-MSCP interface

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.0.0
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    First release
